ISIS thugs are shown smashing shrines and statues in the UNESCO World Heritage city of Hatra . 
  Militants use sledgehammers and AK-47 rifles to destroy ancient relics in the 2,000-year old city . 
  The UN has called the destruction of relics a 'war crime' in the Iraqi city . 
  ISIS claim ancient relics are 'false idols' that violate Islamic law . 
 